column5: I just noticed,  That's all.  Congrats!
Congrats Joey.Thats alot of posts you've been stocking(Snag).  After all those posts I have to ask is there cold beer in the cooler with you.  Mike

Holy crap, I didn't even notice, thanks Snag, actully, I need six more  .  And there's nothing wrong with a good ole stalker once in awhile, keeps ya on your toes:lol:    Gawd, I really gotta get a life eh  Cheers.  Joey
Joey,to much time on your hands  WTG.  Steve
Way to go Joey...2000 posts and a stalker!  lol  blyght
Very, very close....  Just a few more posts will do it...  Mike

WTG Joey. Never notice the post count for myself as its right in my face how much Wayne.Lew,MuskyBill,Roy have and it is not a race I would enter. It was nice to advance to a different (Netman/boy) kinda a name when it happened. Only time I truly cared was when we changed over to this new board and all started anew again for a lil bit. Sorry...dont know what Im talking about.... Congrats Joey....... ps....BEWARE OF STALKERS) PeteNCharmaine
Yep p2k !  Woo hoo .... merry christmas  Uh oh .. I think the Neo Citrin is going to my head  ... along with the scotch and Tylenol
Cool.  Keep the posts coming Jo.

Yep, an all knowing angler    Funny I should hit that milestone on my worst year of fishing    Well the new year is just around the corner, I can feel the fish love  C'mom Mepps, you can do it  Cheers,  Joey
mmmmmkay...  In unrelated news, This just in!  Bellbottoms are in style again!  MUAHAH

well that's great  when I first read it I thought she got looped and crash her car into 2000 posts  or crashed into them because  snag was stalking her  glad I was wrong.....LOL well you know with all the great things that are happening to her I expect to hear this next    the new wonder women is   or something like that...lol
Wouldn't it be easier to start a thread saying what Joey hasn't done this month?? Way to go girl!!!
....and to think I thought this was about Joey driving home from the local pub.
Ya know Chris, I was thinking along the same lines, just could not come up with anything, lol.  Oh, and btw, congrats Joey.
OMG Terry, That's hilarious.  You're gonna pay for that mister  Joey
